title: Trendercaster 8/6: Thailand, Mike DeWine, NBA, Mulan x Tenet, Cameron Diaz
itunes:title: Trendercaster 8/6: Thailand, Mike DeWine, NBA, Mulan x Tenet, Cameron Diaz
description:
On this edition of Trendercaster Jack and Miles discuss Trump pronouncing Thailand like "Thigh-land", the Governor of Ohio has tested positive for COVID-19, the boys discuss more NBA Bubble news, Mulan is being released on Disney+ while Tenet is still slated for theatrical release, and Cameron Diaz sat down with Gwyneth Paltrow to discuss how hard it is to be an actor.
